    47                                  
    48                                  ;calling conventions for msvcrt
    49                                  ;the return value is stored on eax
    50                                  ;the registers eax,ecx,edx volatile registers
    51                                  ;the paramters should be freed by the caller
    52                                  ;the paramters are passed on the stack in reverse order
    53                                  ;printf(
    54                                  ; external function: call[printf]
    55                                  ; internal function call label
